#Computation of the density of LiNbO3

#Dataset 1 : Computation of density
kptopt 1
ngkpt  2 2 2
shiftk 0.5 0.5 0.5
nshiftk 1
prtden 1
toldfe 1.0d-12
ecutsm 0.5

#Definition of material bands
nband 42
nbdbuf 2

#Definition of the atom types
ntypat 3          # 3 types of atoms
znucl 41 3 8      # Nb, Li, O

#Definition of the planewave basis set
ecut 8

#Definition of the SCF procedure
nstep 100
diemac 10

#Definition of the atoms
natom 10          
typat 1 1 2 2 3 3 3 3 3 3 

#Definition of the unit cell
acell 3*10.3915492
angdeg 3*55.857
xred
